This is a port of Ri-Li for the GCW ZERO handheld console.

It is based on ZX81's port of Ri-Li to the Dingoo handheld console which is based on the original source code.

Ri-li is a arcade game licensed under the GPL (General Public License).
You drive a toy wood engine in many levels and you must collect
all the coaches for win. You can download it and play indefinitely.
It's Free. You can play on 'Windows', 'Linux', 'Mac OsX', 'AmigaOS4'.

Full-featured,
- 19 languages: Arabic, Breton, Chinese, English, Esperanto, French,
  German, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Portuguese, Russian, Slovak,
  Spanish, Swedish, Polish, Turkish, Hungarian, Dutch.
- Colorful animated wood engine.
- 50 levels in this first version
- 3 beautiful musics and many sound effects.

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
./configure --host=mipsel/linux --prefix=/opt/gcw0-toolchain/usr/mipsel-gcw0-linux-uclibc/sysroot/usr CXXFLAGS="-DGCWZERO"
